   ALLIED-HONEYWELL-MARKETPLACE (Undated) _ Talks with analysts and
investors elicited relief at the financial terms and immediate
financial prospects of the Allied-Honeywell merger, and a firm
belief that the combined company really will be better than the sum
of its parts. By Claudia H. Deutsch.
