   HKN-SABRES-STARS (Dallas) _ Advance on the Stanley Cup finals,
which begin Tuesday night. Neither the Dallas Stars nor the Buffalo
Sabres have ever won the cup, and it's the Stars who will be
favored. By Joe LaPointe.
