<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990608.0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-08 10:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7031 &Cx1f; tad-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCHUETT-COLUMN09-COX     06-08 0740
