</P>
<P>
   BOOK-PROFILE-EVIL (Undated) _ Former FBI crime analyst Roy
Hazelwood profiles a lifetime of studying crime in his book ``The
Evil That Men Do.'' One of his early cases was the recovery of a
vacuum cleaner that had been missing for years. Luckily, his career
would lead to far more fascinating cases and refinements of
crime-fighting techniques. By MICHAEL LOPEZ.
</P>
