<HEADLINE>
A LOCAL HEIRESS' LEGACY 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   (To purchase this special one-shot feature culled from The New
York Times Syndicate's ``Way To Go!'' travel package _ the rate is
not prohibitive _ contact New York Times Sales Executive DEBRA
WEYDERT at (732) 390-4480; fax, 732-390-4697.) &LR;  &QL; 
