<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    NO COPIER, FEW BOOKS AND DESKS, SCHOOLING DECLINES IN IRAQ
 &HT;    With Photos.
 &HT;    With IRAQ-SANCTIONS-$ADV13.
 &HT;    For Use Sun., June 13 And Thereafter.
