NYT-06-08-99 1224EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990608.0112 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-08 12:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7172 &Cx1f; tad-z
s t &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MONTSERRAT-VOLCANO-$A     06-08 1645
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MONTSERRAT-VOLCANO-$ADV13-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FOUR YEARS AFTER VOLCANO ERUPTION, MONTSERRAT FUMBLES THROUGH
THE ASH
 &HT;    1100&AMP;ADD
 &HT;    With Photos.
 &HT;    With MONTSERRAT-EXPATS-$ADV13; MONTSERRAT-BOX-$ADV13.
