<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-08 15:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7405 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OLIPHANT-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      06-08 0757
