<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-08 20:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7853 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BAREFOOT-PARTIES-LADN     06-08 3506
