<P>
   TRIPLE-SLAYING (Seattle) _ Three people are dead at a Seattle
home daycare. The mother, adult daughter and 10-year-old grandchild
of the mother are dead, apparently shot to death. A newborn and
another young child were taken unharmed from the home and admitted
to hospital for observation.
