oils sold under the Spectrum label. (Peter DaSilva/New York Times
Photo) LITE
</P>
<P>
   (NYT8) NEW YORK -- June 8, 1999 -- GREEN-TOMATOES, 6-8 -- Green
tomatoes for sale at a farmer's market in Manhattan's Union Square.
Anyone who is panting for the local tomato season to begin has
already missed its opening. For true tomato fans, the season begins
when the first green tomatoes arrive at the markets. And they have.
(Jeffery A. Salter/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
